channel.title: Please help Webclient Troubles
channel.description:
Can anyone help me make a webclient for my server? I have the required Server and webhost for the webclient, I have attempted making one on my own, but can't seem to find the right things, I would love too see my server get online through a webclient.
If anyone is willing to help me out through teamviewer.. Or you can Skype me .. It would be much appreciated, I do not have much, but I can find out a way to pay the favor.
Thanks, Viz Curse
P.S - Skype Name is Cade.Prohm

item.title: Please help Webclient Troubles
item.dc:creator: @joelandjacob joelandjacob
item.description:
@joelandjacob wrote:

Try using http://www.rswebclients.org.

It auto-creates a webclient for your server. If you have custom items, you might want to look up a webclient guide like Ric’s Webclient Tutorial. He explains it indepth, and is very simple.
